name: Marty McFly from Back to the Future

modelVersions.description:
All of my embeddings are trained with v1-5-pruned-emaonly with the vae-ft-mse-840000-ema-pruned.vae.pt VAE

Images use the consistentFactor_v3Light model. This used to be included in the metadata for the images on this site but they just removed that field for some reason.
